Paso 2. Descarga de datos de presncia de GBIF

Cargamos las librerias, descargamos las variables bioclimaticas (10km^2) y altitud

#install.packages("raster")#Lo reinstalamos para solucionar problema con getdata
library(raster)
## Warning: package 'raster' was built under R version 4.2.1
## Loading required package: sp
clim10km<- getData('worldclim', var = "bio", res = 5)
## Warning in getData("worldclim", var = "bio", res = 5): getData will be removed in a future version of raster
## . You can use access these data, and more, with functions from the geodata package instead
plot(clim10km)

alt <- getData('alt', country='ESP', mask=FALSE)
plot(alt)
